graph TD
    A[User opens Supply modal] --> B{Asset has<br/>e-mode categories?}
    B -->|No| C[Normal supply flow<br/>no collateral selector]
    B -->|Yes| D[Show collateral options]

    D --> E[User picks a tier]

    E --> F{Same as current<br/>e-mode?}
    F -->|Yes| G[Just supply<br/>nothing else changes]

    F -->|No| H{Switching to<br/>Default / no e-mode?}

    H -->|Yes| I{Does user have collateral<br/>on assets with 0% base LTV?}
    I -->|Yes| J[BLOCKED<br/>Assets only work as collateral<br/>inside e-mode]
    I -->|No| K[Check borrows]

    H -->|No| K

    K --> L{Does user have<br/>borrows?}
    L -->|Yes| M{All borrows allowed<br/>in new tier?}
    M -->|No| N[BLOCKED<br/>Incompatible borrows]
    M -->|Yes| O[Continue]
    L -->|No| O

    O --> P{Does user have collateral<br/>on other assets?}
    P -->|No| Q[Continue]
    P -->|Yes| R{Would any asset get<br/>0% LTV in new tier?}
    R -->|Yes| S[BLOCKED<br/>Collateral would lose LTV]
    R -->|No| Q

    Q --> T{Would health factor<br/>drop below 1.0?}
    T -->|Yes| U[BLOCKED<br/>Liquidation risk]
    T -->|No| V[Switch tier + supply<br/>bundled in one transaction]

    G --> W[Supply succeeds]
    V --> W

    style J fill:#e76f51,color:#fff
    style N fill:#e76f51,color:#fff
    style S fill:#e76f51,color:#fff
    style U fill:#e76f51,color:#fff
    style W fill:#2a9d8f,color:#fff
    style C fill:#2a9d8f,color:#fff
    style G fill:#2a9d8f,color:#fff
